call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Haliburton's (IND) pass goes out of bounds and is not touched by any player on ATL.
Murray (ATL) reaches in and any contact with Haliburton's (IND) arm is marginal.
Hield (IND) is in a legal guarding position during Murray's (ATL) drive to the basket and makes clean contact with the ball when he reaches in.  Any further contact with Murray is incidental.
Hield (IND) jumps vertically and although he lowers his left arm, he absorbs the body contact with Bey (ATL) during the shot attempt.
Bogdanovic (ATL) briefly places a hand on Hield's (IND) arm as he makes a move on the perimeter and the contact is marginal.

Replay review of the foul called on Murray (ATL) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Murray (ATL) abnormally extends his right leg during his jump shot attempt and initiates more than marginal contact with Toppin (IND) as he defends the play.
Haliburton (IND) and Young (ATL) briefly engage and disengage on the perimeter.
Young (ATL) does not initiate any illegal contact with Haliburton (IND) during his drive to the basket, and he loses control of the ball on his own.
Nesmith (IND) jumps alongside of Murray (ATL) during his driving shot attempt and the body contact after he releases the shot is incidental.
